Package pkgMain

Class Plot

java.lang.Object
pkgMain.Plot
public class Plot
extends java.lang.Object
The main plot where the user is able to drag plants from the basket and add it to the garden as they please. Draws from: https://docs.oracle.com/javafx/2/drag_drop/HelloDragAndDrop.java.html and https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/javafx/events-tutorial/paper-doll.htm
Author:
Matthew
